CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 4, 1960, pg. 9 reads: "Beaver Valley "Pros" - Beaver Valley Progressive Cosmetologists made their debut recently with an impressive membership tea at Triedstone Baptist Church. Members, standing left to right, are Mmes. Grace Simmons, Zella Poindexter, Thelma Witherspoon, Lena Thomas, president; Sara Reddick, Ruth Brown, Opra Henderson, Lottie Bazemore, Clara Jenkins and Jessie Dawson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing dark dress with full skirt and light colored collar, hat with wide brim, and corsage, standing next to table in Triedstone Baptist Church for Beaver Valley Progressive Cosmetologists membership tea, Beaver
